  "text": "In this part, we survey the work related to knowledge acquisition according to the three challenges addressed by this approach. The more significant is undoubtedly the exploration problem since it is the one which concentrates a large part of the literature. Although the amount of work is more timorous, we will see that state representation can also take advantage of an active search for knowledge and that maximizing empowerment is generally sufficient to produce interesting behaviors. We focus our study on recent work and recommend to the interested reader to look at [CITATION_1] for an overview on older methods on knowledge acquisition in RL.",
